<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FFC56A7AF7F693BF1763BC29" pageId="62" pageNumber="820" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFFC56A7AF7F693BF1763BC29" blockId="62.[2058,2651,1392,1819]" pageId="62" pageNumber="820">
Treated in Nycterikaupius by H. Menu in 1987. Often included in 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFC56A7AF68790481417BD1C" baseAuthorityName="Thomas" baseAuthorityYear="1901" box="[2427,2583,1553,1582]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Neoromicia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="62" pageNumber="819" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="somalica">N. somalica</taxonomicName>
, but separated by I. LL. Rautenbach and colleagues in 1993, based on chromosomal differences. Populations of north-eastern 
<collectingCountry id="BC83766EFFC56A7AF7F090EA1691BDFE" box="[2060,2193,1715,1740]" name="Botswana" pageId="62" pageNumber="820">Botswana</collectingCountry>
, northern 
<collectingCountry id="BC83766EFFC56A7AF6B890EA17BDBDFE" box="[2372,2493,1715,1740]" name="Namibia" pageId="62" pageNumber="820">Namibia</collectingCountry>
, and perhaps 
<collectingCountry id="BC83766EFFC56A7AF7A8908A16B9BDC6" box="[2132,2233,1747,1780]" name="Angola" pageId="62" pageNumber="820">Angola</collectingCountry>
may represent a valid subspecies, vansoni. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
